I've been thinking about such ``algorithm multiplications'' for a long
time, but I never decided to start coding up one.
What about DES * IDEA * MDC (Peter Gutmann's code to turn secure one-way
hash functions into CFB conventional ciphers) ?  I believe that combining
very different ciphers is the key.

